OL,6,FA severely disabled teenager faces an
OL,7,Funcertain future after her mother's
OL,8,Fapplication was rejected by the courts
OL,9,Fto advocate on her behalf.
OL,11,FRuby was diagnosed with a rare
OL,12,Fchromosome disorder, Idic 15, at just
OL,13,Fsix months old, and needs round the
OL,14,Fclock care.
