OL,3,CCourt rejects bid by mum to be
OL,4,Cconsulted over her daughter's care
OL,6,FRuby's mother, Alison Parr, describes
OL,7,Fthe physical pain in her chest as a
OL,8,Fresult of "anxiety and fear" and says
OL,9,Fit is something she has had since a
OL,10,Fcourt rejected her recent application
OL,11,Fto be consulted over her daughter's
OL,12,Fcare.
OL,14,FFor 17 years she has been Ruby's main
OL,15,Fcarer, but that changes when she turns
OL,16,F18 and Alison says she is "terrified
OL,17,Ffor the future."
OL,19,FAlison said: "I can list over the
OL,20,Fyears the things that have happened in
OL,21,Fterms of Ruby's care.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
