OL,3,CCourt rejects bid by mum to be
OL,4,Cconsulted over her daughter's care
OL,6,F"Without me Ruby's quality of life
OL,7,Fwouldn't be what it is or she wouldn't
OL,8,Feven be here - that's why this
OL,9,Fdeputyship is needed, and so important
OL,10,Ffor me - so I can keep her safe."
OL,12,FIn February, Ruby who cannot speak or
OL,13,Fwrite, was pursued by the health
OL,14,Fservice and threatened with a fine
OL,15,Fafter she was prescribed new
OL,16,Fmedication.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
