OL,3,CCourt rejects bid by mum to be
OL,4,Cconsulted over her daughter's care
OL,6,FThe government says the Mental
OL,7,FCapacity Act provides sufficient
OL,8,Fprotection to ensure Ruby's best
OL,9,Finterests are met.
OL,11,FRuby and her mum were not in court and
OL,12,Fthe judge's decision to reject the
OL,13,Fapplication for deputyship was based
OL,14,Fon a written submission, in which
OL,15,FAlison said she tried her best to
OL,16,Fdescribe her daughter's complex needs.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/11
