OL,3,CCourt rejects bid by mum to be
OL,4,Cconsulted over her daughter's care
OL,6,FThe family wanted Ruby to be able to
OL,7,Fstay at home with her brothers when
OL,8,Fshe turns 18, but care providers say
OL,9,Fthey can't meet her needs there and
OL,10,Fshe will have to move into residential
OL,11,Fcare.
OL,13,FRuby is on her eighth social worker in
OL,14,Frecent years, but her mum will no
OL,15,Flonger be consulted over her medical
OL,16,Ftreatment and welfare.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/11
