OL,3,CCourt rejects bid by mum to be
OL,4,Cconsulted over her daughter's care
OL,6,FThe family's MP in Congleton, Sarah
OL,7,FRussell said in a statement: "I've
OL,8,Fbeen appalled by the continued
OL,9,Fhardship that Alison and her daughter,
OL,10,FRuby, have had to endure in recent
OL,11,Fmonths.
OL,13,F"It appears every obstacle has been
OL,14,Fput in their way, and I can only begin
OL,15,Fto imagine how that feels to
OL,16,Fexperience first-hand.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
