OL,3,CCourt rejects bid by mum to be
OL,4,Cconsulted over her daughter's care
OL,6,F"I appreciate that there is a legal
OL,7,Fprocess to be followed, but it can't
OL,8,Fbe sustainable for already vulnerable
OL,9,Ffamilies to exhaust their emotional
OL,10,Fand financial resources to take agency
OL,11,Fover their own care.
OL,13,F"Ruby has incredibly complex needs,
OL,14,Fneeds for which care has been tailored
OL,15,Fwith love by her mother, Alison. As I
OL,16,Funderstand, the last few years have
OL,17,Falready been challenging and
OL,18,Finconsistent. We have discussed the
OL,19,Fimpact that real-life mistakes, such
OL,20,Fas the prescription error, can have.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
