OL,3,CCourt rejects bid by mum to be
OL,4,Cconsulted over her daughter's care
OL,6,F"The last thing that Ruby needs is
OL,7,Ffurther uncertainty. Having provided
OL,8,Fcare for her daughter for almost
OL,9,Feighteen years, Alison knows Ruby's
OL,10,Fneeds better than anyone."
OL,12,FA Ministry of Justice spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid in response to Ruby's family's
OL,14,Fconcerns: "We cannot comment on
OL,15,Fdecisions made by the independent
OL,16,Fjudiciary.
OL,18,F"The Mental Capacity Act allows a
OL,19,Fcarer, such as a relative to make
OL,20,Fdecisions around care without the need
OL,21,Ffor deputyship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
