OL,6,F"Deputies are generally appointed for
OL,7,Fmatters relating to property and
OL,8,Faffairs. Legal assistance is not
OL,9,Fnecessary for applications to the
OL,10,FCourt of Protection."
OL,12,FAlison says she felt she 'had no
OL,13,Foption' but to appoint solicitors to
OL,14,Fapply for the deputyship, adding that
OL,15,Fthe language used in the forms and the
OL,16,Fcourts "isn't language they use" and
OL,17,Fthe issue was so important to their
OL,18,Floved ones, they had to pay for
OL,19,Fsolicitors to act on their behalf.
